@startuml onboarding-flow
title Webtensor Onboarding — Reading Order

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #555
skinparam DefaultFontName "Segoe UI"

start

:You arrived at the repo;

if (What do you want to do?) then (Use it / understand it)
  :README.md;
  :docs/onboarding/00-start-here.md;
  :docs/onboarding/01-system-walkthrough.md;
  if (Need more depth?) then (yes)
    :docs/onboarding/02-package-deep-dive.md;
    :docs/architecture.md (canonical);
    :docs/ir-reference.md (canonical);
  endif
elseif (Add an op / kernel) then (contribute)
  :docs/onboarding/07-contributor-guide.md;
  :docs/adding-an-op.md (canonical recipe);
  :docs/onboarding/03-backends-and-kernels.md;
elseif (Pick something to fix) then (fix bugs)
  :docs/onboarding/06-bugs-and-gaps.md;
  :docs/onboarding/05-state-of-the-project.md;
elseif (Plan bigger work) then (refactor / rearchitect)
  :docs/onboarding/05-state-of-the-project.md;
  :docs/onboarding/08-rearchitect-notes.md;
  :docs/next.md (roadmap);
else (just curious about autograd)
  :docs/onboarding/04-autograd.md;
endif

:Then dive into the code;
stop

@enduml
